      *Still not sure if it's for you? Send me an email at <a
        href="mailto:me@jamesqquick.com"
        class="cursor font-bold">me@jamesqquick.com</a
      > with any outstanding questions!
    </p>
    <div
      id="newsletter"
      class={`bg-gradient-to-r p-2 from-blue-800 to-purple-800 mt-20  rounded-3xl  mx-auto`}
    >
      <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-3xl py-8 px-4 md:px-8 md:py-16">
